reviewText:
A very fun kart racing game available on PC:
*Solid mechanics;
*Good controls (although using a controller is a must);
*Decent presentation;
*The soundtrack is fitting;
*Runs smoothly.

My only major complaint is that it is a bit too easy.
I still think you should be able to unlock content even when playing online with a friend, but I digress.

It's a great game, I definitely recommend it if you're looking for an arcade racing game or a serviceable substitute for Mario Kart.

